行歌手将在今年纽约皇后区的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-killers-post-malone-and-sza-to-headline-governors-ball-2024-3571686">州长</a>舞会以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vampire-weekend-hozier-noah-kahan-to-headline-hinterland-festival-2024-3574104">辛特兰音乐节上</a>表演。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-announces-2024-uk-and-european-tour-buy-tickets-3596432">Chappell Roan 宣布 2024 年英国和欧洲巡演的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
最后的晚宴派对对他们首张专辑的回应以及从圣文森特汲取灵感https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-on-the-response-to-debut-album-and-st-vincent-inspiration-3596430?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=最后的晚餐派对对首张专辑和圣文森特灵感的回应Liberty DunworthMon, 04 Mar 2024 14:29:27 +0000 Music InterviewsMusic NewsNewsBRIT AwardsIndiePopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3596430 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party-brits@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party-brits@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party-brits@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party-brits@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party-brits@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party-brits@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party-brits@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乐队在 2024 年全英音乐盛典红地毯上接受 NME 采访，并透露艺术家的灵感来自于《Prelude To Ecstasy》中的一首曲目</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-on-the-response-to-debut-album-and-st-vincent-inspiration-3596430">关于他们首张专辑的回应以及从 St Vincent 汲取灵感的《The Last Evening Party》帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party-brits@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party-brits@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party-brits@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party-brits@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party-brits@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party-brits@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party-brits@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">最后的晚宴派对</a>回顾了他们的首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-debut-album-prelude-to-ecstasy-release-new-single-on-your-side-listen-preorder-3528044">“Prelude To Ecstasy”</a>的巨大反响，并透露<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/st-vincent">圣文森特</a>是他们其中一首歌曲的灵感来源。观看我们对上面乐队的采访视频。</p><p>在本周末（3 月 2 日）的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">全英音乐奖</a>红毯上，这支英国乐队在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-brits-announce-2024-rising-star-winner-3555457">获得新星奖</a>前不久与<em>NME</em>进行了交流。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/the-last-dinner-party-live-in-london-setlist-photos-3581176">伦敦最后的晚宴现场：巴洛克流行极简主义者夺取王位</a></strong></li></ul><p>回顾他们的 LP 所获得的巨大反响——该<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-score-biggest-number-one-debut-album-in-nine-years-3585175">专辑成为近十年来最大的首张专辑</a>——乐队回忆起他们对积极反馈浪潮的“惊讶”感。</p><p> “我们甚至没有把它列入我们的愿望清单，因为它太荒谬了，”节奏吉他手 Lizzie Mayland 承认。 “所以我们非常感激，[这一切]都是如此超现实。”</p><p>主唱阿比盖尔·莫里斯还回顾了​​乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-2024-european-tour-dates-buy-tickets-3531799">最近在 2024 年初的欧洲巡演</a>，并将登上舞台的感觉描述为“天堂”。</p><p> “唱片出来了，我们就直接开始巡演了。这是我们做过的最好的旅行，因为这是人们第一次知道所有事物的单词，”她解释道。 “那真的非常非常美丽。”</p><p>最后的晚宴派对在颁奖典礼前被确认<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-brits-announce-2024-rising-star-winner-3555457">获得全英新星奖</a>，并于当晚由圣文森特颁奖。乐队分享了对这位美国歌手、词曲作者和吉他手的钦佩，并向<em>NME</em>讲述了这位艺术家如何为他们专辑的部分内容提供灵感。</p><p> “她是我们喜爱的令人惊叹的歌曲和连复段的创作者。我还为她弹吉他！”吉他手艾米丽·罗伯茨 (Emily Roberts) 说道，并接着解释了如何在《欢庆前奏曲》中听到圣文森特的影响。 </p><figure id="attachment_3596440" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3596440" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3596440" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270.jpg" alt="《最后的晚宴派对》的乔治亚·戴维斯、阿比盖尔·莫里斯、艾米丽·罗伯茨、莉齐·梅兰和奥罗拉·尼舍夫奇于 2024 年 3 月 2 日在英国伦敦 O2 体育馆出席 2024 年全英音乐奖颁奖典礼。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Last-Dinner-Party@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3596440" class="wp-caption-text"> 《最后的晚宴派对》的乔治亚·戴维斯、阿比盖尔·莫里斯、艾米丽·罗伯茨、莉齐·梅兰和奥罗拉·尼舍夫奇于 2024 年 3 月 2 日在英国伦敦 O2 体育馆出席 2024 年全英音乐奖颁奖典礼。 （摄影：Karwai Tang/WireImage/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p> “尤其是在《罪人》中。她的一首名为《Marrow》的歌曲（收录在与 David Byrne 合作的专辑《Brass Tactics》中）启发了我为《Sinner》写的吉他线，”她解释道。 “所以她是一个大灵感！”</p><p>圣文森特本人也在红地毯上发表了支持言论， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/st-vincent-on-her-love-for-the-last-dinner-party-and-what-to-expect-from-her-new-album-3596314">称赞乐队的专辑“富有冒险精神、浪漫而富有戏剧性”</a> 。</p><p>在<em>NME</em>的采访中，The Last Evening Party 表达了他们对参加颁奖典礼的其他艺术家的钦佩，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cmat">CMAT</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kylie-minogue">Kylie Minogue</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/caroline-polachek">Caroline Polachek</a> ，并暗示新音乐已经即将出现。</p><p>莫里斯调侃的其中一首歌曲是“Big Dog”——尽管从未在他们的任何官方录音室版本中出现过，但它已经成为乐队粉丝的最爱。</p><p>上个月在与<em>《每日星报》</em>的讨论中谈到这首期待已久的歌曲时，莫里斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-want-snoop-dogg-to-feature-on-big-dog-3581899">暗示这首歌可能是众星云集的合作</a>。 “我们已经讨论过让<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/snoop-dogg">史努比狗狗</a>参与一首诗，”她说。 “《大狗》是一首被诅咒的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nine-inch-nails">九英寸钉子</a>遇到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-waits">汤姆·威茨</a>情境的一首歌。我们希望史努比为此写一首诗。”</p><p>在乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-speak-out-on-privilege-respond-to-cost-of-living-comments-being-taken-out-of-context-3595426">公开谈论他们的“特权”之后，也出现了新音乐的暗示，以回应有关病毒式传播的生活成本危机的“断章取义”的引用</a>。</p><p>在全英音乐节获胜后，这支伦敦乐队和<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-radar/the-nme-100-essential-emerging-artists-for-2023-radar-3372061">NME 100 校友</a>将踏上一系列<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-extensive-2024-us-tour-buy-tickets-3575005">美国头条秀</a>和随后的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-add-three-shows-to-2024-uk-and-ireland-tour-due-to-phenomenal-demand-3584408">英国巡演之旅。</a>您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fthe-last-dinner-party-tickets%2Fartist%2F2937467" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>找到美国演出的门票， <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fthe-last-dinner-party-tickets%2Fartist%2F5395177" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>找到英国演出的门票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-on-the-response-to-debut-album-and-st-vincent-inspiration-3596430">关于他们首张专辑的回应以及从 St Vincent 汲取灵感的《The Last Evening Party》帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
